item.title: Demonoid is back!
item.dc:creator: hypnotek
item.description:
Above all, I have to say demonoid is most useful for getting audio books and really cool packs of wallpapers. They have some really cool stuff on there from people who just find the coolest stuff and then upload them. First thing I did when it came back up, downloaded a pack of 200 widescreen wallpapers. If anyone wants me to send them the rar, i’d be happy to oblige, they’re all really cool.

But on a more serious note, I want to publicly apologize for what I said about JohnKiller. It really was a whole new low, and I should have respected his opinion rather than call him out and attack him for it. I hope we can move on from this and leave John and everyone on his side of the argument alone, and I also hope that the same will come from anyone against piracy. I’m sorry if this came out as something unproductive and very much like a trollbait/flame war, and I hope everyone can accept my apology and continue to be a strong supporter of black mesa!
